# Aider privacy guard -- defense in depth (KNOWLEDGE_MAP §6 / H8 ADR-0023).
# This repo is PRIVATE and cloud-whitelisted for aider delegation, BUT the Ryzen
# memory archive below holds sovereign content (vault + personal session memory)
# that must never reach a cloud LLM. aider honors .aiderignore for BOTH auto-context
# and explicit `aider <file>` adds, covering every wrapper (local + cloud) at once --
# preferred over a per-path check in the 6 .cmd cloud wrappers (anti-pattern #11:
# fragile batch path-matching across security-critical files).
